data.description: In an estate. Location survey has been ordered. Almost an acre goes back to trees of Hillcrest Park. Hardwood floors, newer bathroom, nice kitchen cabinets, 25x25 screened-in porch, one basement window is larger, newer roof, newer pole garage with heat & electric 2019, large attached garage. The laundry room could be a 3rd BR by moving laundry to basement. This room has a window and a closet. Average utilities: Duke $198.83, Water $20.00-$25.00, Centerpoint $39.18; includes the house and two garages, which have window A/C and heat.
